snippet.title: Sailor Moon RevengeX - PlayStation 2 Homebrew
snippet.description:
Released in 2021 and developed by Nova32 Animation Studios, this unofficial Sailor Moon beat'em up is a homebrew game for the SEGA Dreamcast, PlayStation Portable and, interestingly, PlayStation 2.

Download: https://nova32-entertainment.itch.io/sailor-moon-revengex
